data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The main contrast bug is CSS specificity: `.topnav nav a` is overriding the primary button text color, which makes the phone CTA muted instead of high-contrast. I’m patching that directly and tightening the button states so every primary CTA keeps readable text across nav, hero, contact, and form states."}

